org.apache.pdfbox.preflight.graphic

Enum ColorSpaces

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ColorSpaces>
      • org.apache.pdfbox.preflight.graphic.ColorSpaces
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ColorSpaces>

    public enum ColorSpaces
extends Enum<ColorSpaces>
    This enum makes ColorSpaces validation easier. Labels represent ColorSpace names as defined in the "PDF Reference 1.4".
